casebody.data:
Wednesday, August 18, 1999

MOTION DOCKET

97-1111. State v. Stojetz.

Madison C.P. No. 96CR10086. This cause came on for further consideration upon appellant’s application for reopening under S.CtPrac.R. XI(5). Upon consideration thereof,

IT IS ORDERED by the court that the application for reopening under S.CtPrac.R. XI(5) be, and hereby is, denied.
